<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Docker on Josia's Blog</title><link>https://jscheytt.github.io/tags/docker/</link><description>Recent content in Docker on Josia's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><copyright>Josia Scheytt</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 23 Jul 2021 14:42:07 +0200</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://jscheytt.github.io/tags/docker/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Docker does not really help you a lot trying to get permissions right</title><link>https://jscheytt.github.io/p/docker-does-not-really-help-you-a-lot-trying-to-get-permissions-right/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jul 2021 14:42:07 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://jscheytt.github.io/p/docker-does-not-really-help-you-a-lot-trying-to-get-permissions-right/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;I really love Docker, and I also come to like security more and more.
One advice I have been hearing a lot (e.g. in this &lt;a class="link" href="https://snyk.io/blog/10-docker-image-security-best-practices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Container Security Cheat Sheet from Snyk&lt;/a&gt;) is that &lt;strong&gt;you should not run your container as a root user&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Easy thing,&amp;rdquo; I thought to myself, &amp;ldquo;I am just going to put something like &lt;code&gt;USER {app}&lt;/code&gt;&amp;rdquo; at the top of my Dockerfile.&amp;quot;
Well, think again, because:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-Dockerfile" data-lang="Dockerfile"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;node:lts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;USER&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;node&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# I would have thought that after this point, every action will happen in the name of this user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# and also that every created directory and file will belong to this user ... 😕 But:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# ⚠️ This directory is created by root:root!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;WORKDIR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;/app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# ⚠️ These files will be copied over to be owned by root:root!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; package*.json ./&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# 💥 This step fails in some (not all!) environments with errors like &amp;#34;Not enough permissions on /app&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; npm install &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="se"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; npm run verify&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# ⚠️ If you manage to get to this point, these files, too, will be copied over to be owned by root:root!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; . .&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;ENTRYPOINT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;npm&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;I ended up fixing it by creating the directory and then &lt;code&gt;chown&lt;/code&gt;-ing it.
Equally I executed the &lt;code&gt;COPY&lt;/code&gt; instructions with the &lt;code&gt;--chown&lt;/code&gt; flag.
In the end I refactored it a bit using some &lt;code&gt;ENV&lt;/code&gt;s, too:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-Dockerfile" data-lang="Dockerfile"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;node:lts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# Ensure that target WORKDIR exists and is owned by target (non-root) user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;ENV&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;USERNAME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;node
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;ENV&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;USERID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$USERNAME&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$USERNAME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;ENV&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;TARGETDIR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/app&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; mkdir -p &lt;span class="nv"&gt;$TARGETDIR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; chown -R &lt;span class="nv"&gt;$USERID&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;$TARGETDIR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;WORKDIR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;$TARGETDIR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;USER&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;$USERNAME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; --chown&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$USERID&lt;/span&gt; package*.json ./&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; npm install &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="se"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; npm run verify&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; --chown&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$USERID&lt;/span&gt; . .&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;ENTRYPOINT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;npm&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>